Description: Provides tools to process genomic input files, compute pairwise linkage
    disequilibrium, define haplotype blocks (haploblocks), estimate local genomic estimated
    breeding values (localGEBV), visualize marker, haploblock, and localGEBV patterns,
    and optimize parent selection for genomic selection with a genetic algorithm workflow.
